Provide accurate estimates for scope of work/prices for all manufactured components/assemblies through the manufacturing department:
Provide support through proper information utilizing outside vendors for any material/hardware pricing and ensuring that all estimates reflect current and precise quoting on the scope of work outlined;
Thoroughly comprehend the Bill of Materials (BOMs) and have a strong understanding of any required special outside processes;
Utilization of CAD software to review sales and engineering drawings.
